Package org.tms.api.io.options

Options to import and export Tables to a variety of formats.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DateTimeFormatIOOption
    A BaseIOOptions where the output can have a date-time displayed in the output footer.
    PageableIOOption
    An BaseIOOptions where the output can be paged.
    StyleableIOOption
    An BaseIOOptions where the output can be Styled.
    TitleableIOOption
    An BaseIOOptions where the output can be titled.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseIOOptions<T extends BaseIOOptions<T>>
    The base class for all IOOptions, which facilitate the import and export of Tables to other file formats.
    CSVOptions  
    DocOptions  
    FormattedPageIOOptions<T extends FormattedPageIOOptions<T>>
    The base class that BaseIOOptions that support formatted and paged export output.
    HTMLOptions  
    PDFOptions  
    RTFOptions  
    StyledPageIOOptions<T extends StyledPageIOOptions<T>>
    The base class that BaseIOOptions that support display styling extend.
    TitledPageIOOptions<T extends TitledPageIOOptions<T>>
    The base class that BaseIOOptions that support titles extend.
    TMSOptions  
    XlsOptions  
    XMLOptions  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IOFileFormat
    The external file formats that TMS Tables can be exported to and, in some cases, imported from.
